{"tid":2242851,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"勞力是無止境 人總要向上嗎","createTime":"2020-10-14T10:11:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T10:20:56.000Z","uid":77235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4c833fe441102a326989749d8fc4ff1da8e27659","tid":2242851,"uid":77235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:11:26.000Z","msg":"十零歲要諗自己既成績 要升咩大學 要讀咩科 要有夢想要有目標<br />\n出左社會 日日要OT 放工要進修要考牌 博考乜師物師 <br />\n考完牌又要博升職 又要諗過塘<br />\n去到某個年紀 人工頂左又要諗創業 學人做網店 寫blog 拍vlog搵額外收入<br />\n明明有幾千萬資產收租收息 足夠應付家庭開支有餘 又要諗人地有幾億幾十億幾百億資產<br />\n真係有放假既時候 又要去social 要睇書 要周圍睇下個世界<br />\n去屎坑都要帶住個電話 唔可以浪費任何一秒接收資訊既機會<br />\n甚至訓教都唔可以訓得耐 人地訓5-6個鐘 你訓8個鐘已經係懶<br />\n究竟要上進要比較要努力到幾時 係咪除左死唔可以有安寧既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5508bf54ce17191324a7bace897ac139d5fe78","tid":2242851,"uid":4727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:14:40.000Z","msg":"起左你底好似幾有錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0714f2537dfb1b5bc6c1eef6235df5f3d4135542","tid":2242851,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd5508bf54ce17191324a7bace897ac139d5fe78","tid":2242851,"uid":4727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:14:40.000Z","msg":"起左你底好似幾有錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:17:38.000Z","msg":"點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ff6c9d2da392b11fbfc3f9c786c32f208e181d","tid":2242851,"uid":378793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:19:04.000Z","msg":"不枉這生需按照誰方向<br />\n每一天都有所為才能毋負過晚上<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83f47d321c0c26494ab479175980539144fa789","tid":2242851,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:20:56.000Z","msg":"煩緊買邊款Richard Mille <br />\n<br />\n我明你感受"}]}